      "text": "Tas KUNGS fazzija\nridsan us Mohsu eeksch Midi-\nnas: Eij/atgreesees uhs Egip-\ns-Semmi/ jo wiſſi tee Wihti/\ns tawu Dshwibu mekleja/ irr\nmitruschi.\n"
