      "text": "Tad nehme Mohsus fawu\nSeetwu/ un fawus Dehluß/ un\nke tohs us Ehseteem jaht/ un\ngreesahs uhs Egiptes-Semmi/\nn Mohsus nehme to DeewaSis-\nfawa Rohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\ns Mohsu: Peeraugi/ kad tu etj\ngreessamees uhsEgiptes-Sem-\ni/ ka tu wiſſus tohs Brihun-\nus preekfch Waraus darri/ fo\ntew detwis efimu/ tomehr es\nfschu winna Sirdi apzeetina-\nees/ ka wiꞥſch tohs Laudis ne\ntlaidihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tew buhs us Warau\nazziht: Ta fakka tas KUNGS:\nſraels irr mans Dehls/ mans\nPirmdsintajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es efimu us tew faz-\njiis: Atlaid mannu Dehlu/ ka\ntas man kalpo/bet tu eſſi leedsees\nwinnu atlaiſt/Reds/es nokautchu\ntawu Dehlu/ tawu Pirmdsintu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥſch us Zettu\nMahjas-Weeta bija/ nahze wiꞥ-\nnam tas KUNGS pretti/ un\nmekleja winnu nokaut,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Zipora weenu\n(aſſu) Akmini/ un apgrafsija ſa-\nwa Dehla Preekſch-Ahdu/ un\nwiſkare * winna Kahjas; un ta\nfazzija: Tu eſſi man weens Af-\njinn-Bruhdgans.\n* Winna mette to Preekſch-Ahdu preekſch\nMohlus Kahjahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad attahje wiſſch no ta/\nbet ta fazzija: Afﬁnu-Bruhd-\ngans/ tahs Apgrafsichanas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\nus Aarouu: Eij Mohsum pretti\nuhs Tukfnibu. Un wiſſch gabje/\nun fastappe to pee ta Deeiva Kal-\nna/ un wiſſch skuhipſtija to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus Dewe Aaro-\nnam Sinau no wiſſeem Wahr-\ndeem ta KUNGA/ kas winnu\nbij fuhtijis/ un no wiſſahm Siḫ-\nmehm/ ko tas winnam bij pa-\nwehlejis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad gabje Mohsus un A-\narons/ un tee fapulzeja wiſſus\nIsraëka Behrnu Wezzajus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Aarons runnaja wiſ-\nfus tohs Wahrdus/ fo tas\nKUNGS us Mohsu bij runna-\njis/ un wiſſch darrija tahs Sth-\nmes to Lauschu Preekſchā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Laudis tizzeja. Un\ntee dsirdeja ka tas KUNGS tohs\nIsraëka Behrnuu peemekejs/\nun ka tas redſeis winnu Spai-\ndischanas/ un paklannijahs/ un\npeeluhdse (Deewu.)\n"
    }
